item.description:
February 28th 7:00pm meeting at Temple Bar 1688 Massachusetts Avenue, Cambridge, taking over the heart of Liberal New England like a cancer (just kidding).

Please come and meet and talk to a great group of people.
item.how_to_find_us: Please look for John Howe and Thurman Smith; I (Paul Neydavood) will not be able to attend
item.why: Hang out and meet fellow conservatives, and people who lean conservative
